-- ETF Securities Gold ETPs Had $71 Million Inflows Last Week
-- B y   N i c h o l a s   L a r k i n
-- 2012-07-09T13:59:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-09/etf-securities-gold-etps-had-71-million-inflows-last-week.html
ETF Securities Ltd.’s gold-backed
exchange-traded products had $71 million of inflows last week,
the company said in a report e-mailed today.  “The renewed commitment of central banks around the world
to monetary easing reawakened investor fears of currency
debasement, driving inflows into gold,” the company said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nicholas Larkin at 
 nlarkin1@bloomberg.net  